title: #181: Ryan Dawson and The Gang
description: Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  In this special bonus episode Ryan Dawson and friends join me at World Famous Comedy Store it discuss the war on our minds that is going in America today!  From Jussie Smollett to false flags it's all pyscological warfare to get us fighting with one another.  Thank you for all of your support.
